column17: The incident occurred in the Lupaso neighborhood.
column18: 11/27/2017: Assailants set fire to a Seventh Day Adventist Church in Mzuzu, Northern, Malawi. There were no reported casualties. No group claimed responsibility for the incident.
column108: A church was damaged in this attack.
